<%
  gauge_value = 87
  gauge_size = 200
  r = (gauge_size / 2.0) * 0.72
  circ = 2 * Math::PI * r
  arc = circ * 0.75
%>
<section style="min-height: 100dvh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--hv2-bg); padding: 120px 24px 80px; text-align: center;">
  <p style="font-family: var(--hv2-sans); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--hv2-muted); margin: 0 0 24px; animation: hv2-fade-up 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.05s both;">
    Strategic Operating System
  </p>
  <h1 style="font-family: var(--hv2-serif); font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 80px); font-weight: 500; color: var(--hv2-ink); line-height: 1.05; margin: 0 0 28px; max-width: 820px; animation: hv2-fade-up 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.15s both;">
    Turn vision into strategy.<br>Strategy into execution.<br>Execution into momentum.
  </h1>
  <p style="font-family: var(--hv2-sans); font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px); color: var(--hv2-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 14px; max-width: 560px; font-weight: 400; animation: hv2-fade-up 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.28s both;">
    Right now, you don't know if your team's work actually adds up to your goal.
  </p>
  <p style="font-family: var(--hv2-sans); font-size: clamp(14px, 1.6vw, 16px); color: var(--hv2-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 44px; max-width: 480px; opacity: 0.75; animation: hv2-fade-up 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.36s both;">
    Saulto connects your financial systems, runs 10,000 simulated futures, and shows you exactly where you're headed. Then tells every person in the org exactly what to do.
  </p>
  <div class="no-print" style="display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 72px; animation: hv2-fade-up 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.44s both;" data-controller="print">
    <button data-action="click->print#print"
      style="background: var(--hv2-dark); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 100px; padding: 14px 36px; font-family: var(--hv2-sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: 0.03em;">
      Save as PDF
    </button>
  </div>

  <%# Gauge %>
  <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px; animation: hv2-fade-in 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) 0.55s both;"
       data-controller="gauge" data-gauge-value-value="<%= gauge_value %>" data-gauge-size-value="<%= gauge_size %>">
    <div style="position: relative; width: <%= gauge_size %>px; height: <%= (gauge_size * 0.82).round %>px; flex-shrink: 0;">
      <svg width="<%= gauge_size %>" height="<%= (gauge_size * 0.82).round %>" viewBox="0 0 <%= gauge_size %> <%= (gauge_size * 0.82).round %>">
        <circle cx="<%= gauge_size/2 %>" cy="<%= (gauge_size*0.58).round %>" r="<%= r.round %>" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,0,0,0.07)" stroke-width="<%= (gauge_size*0.055).round %>"
          stroke-dasharray="<%= arc.round %> <%= (circ - arc).round %>" stroke-dashoffset="<%= (-arc*0.375).round %>" stroke-linecap="round" />
        <circle data-gauge-target="arc" cx="<%= gauge_size/2 %>" cy="<%= (gauge_size*0.58).round %>" r="<%= r.round %>" fill="none" stroke="var(--hv2-green)" stroke-width="<%= (gauge_size*0.055).round %>"
          stroke-dasharray="0 <%= circ.round %>" stroke-dashoffset="<%= (-arc*0.375).round %>" stroke-linecap="round"
          style="transition: stroke-dasharray 0.04s linear;" />
      </svg>
      <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 2px; left: 0; right: 0; text-align: center;">
        <span data-gauge-target="number" style="font-family: var(--hv2-serif); font-size: <%= (gauge_size * 0.25).round %>px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--hv2-ink); line-height: 1;">0%</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family: var(--hv2-sans); font-size: 13px; color: var(--hv2-muted); margin: 0; letter-spacing: 0.04em;">
      87% confidence of hitting your annual goal
    </p>
    <p style="font-family: var(--hv2-sans); font-size: 11px; color: var(--hv2-muted); margin: 0; opacity: 0.55;">
      Based on 10,000 simulated futures. Updated continuously.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
